			</div>
		</nav>

		<main
			class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 flex-grow relative z-10 pointer-events-auto"
		>
			<div
				class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 auto-rows-[minmax(220px,auto)]"
			>
				<article
					class="glass-card hover-glow lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2 rounded-[2rem] p-10 flex flex-col justify-center group overflow-hidden relative"
				>
					<div
						class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/20 via-blue-900/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none z-0"
					>
					</div>
					<h1
						class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6 text-white relative z-10"
					>
						Costruisco esperienze <br />
						<span
							class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 drop-shadow-md"
							>digitali.</span
						>
					</h1>
					<a
						href="#progetti"
						class="bg-cyan-500/10 hover:bg-cyan-500 border border-cyan-500/30 text-cyan-400 hover:text-slate-950 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 inline-block w-fit relative z-10 backdrop-blur-md"
					>
						Esplora i Lavori
					</a>
				</article>

				<article
					class="glass-card hover-glow lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-1 rounded-[2rem] grid group overflow-hidden"
				>
					<div
						class="col-start-1 row-start-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out group-hover:-translate-y-8 group-hover:opacity-0 z-20 pointer-events-none"
					>
						<div
							class="text-5xl mb-2 drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(6,182,212,0.5)]"
						>
							👨‍💻
						</div>
						<h2
							class="text-4xl font-black tracking-widest text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 drop-shadow-md"
						>
							CHI SONO
						</h2>
						<span
							class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 animate-pulse uppercase bg-slate-900/40 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10"
						>
							<svg
								class="w-4 h-4 text-cyan-400"
								fill="none"
								stroke="currentColor"
								viewBox="0 0 24 24"
								><path
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									stroke-width="2"
									d="M15 15l-2 5L9 9l11 4-5 2zm0 0l5 5M7.188 2.239l.777 2.897M5.136 7.965l-2.898-.777M13.95 4.05l-2.122 2.122m-5.657 5.656l-2.12 2.122"
								></path></svg
							>
							Passa il cursore
						</span>
					</div>

					<div
						class="col-start-1 row-start-1 p-8 flex flex-col justify-center transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out translate-y-8 opacity-0 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100 z-10"
					>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
							<span class="text-3xl">👋</span>
							<h3
								class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight"
							>
								Ciao, sono <span
									class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-500"
									>Samuele Arabia</span>
							</h3>
						</div>
						<p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
							<span
								class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-blue-400 border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-500/10 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mr-2 mb-1 shadow-sm"
							>
								🎓 Ingegnere Informatico
							</span>
							Appassionato di tecnologia fin da bambino, esploro costantemente
							nuovi paradigmi di sviluppo. Il mio obiettivo è trasformare
							idee complesse in interfacce <strong
								class="font-medium text-slate-100"
								>pulite</strong
							> e <strong class="font-medium text-slate-100"
								>performanti</strong
							>.
						</p>
						<p
							class="text-slate-400 text-xs leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-700/50 pt-4 mt-auto flex items-center gap-2"
						>
							<span class="flex-shrink-0 text-cyan-500 text-lg"
								>✨</span
							>
							<span
								><strong
									class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase"
									>CodeForge</strong
								> è la mia fucina digitale per raccogliere e sperimentare
								idee.</span
							>
						</p>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article
					class="glass-card hover-glow lg:col-span-1 lg:row-span-1 rounded-[2rem] p-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center group"
